                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested"><name>Λίπαρος</name></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/>ἔζησεν ἔ
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>τη <num value="75">οε</num> <persName type="attested"><name>Π
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>οσιδώνια</name></persName> <choice><orig>ποι
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>ῖ<reg>ποιι</reg></orig></choice> ἰδίῳ συνβίῳ
                    <lb n="6"/>μνήμης χάριν
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus" resp="#JP">
                <listApp><app><note>Text of Calderone</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Liparos lived 75 years. Posidonia made (this) for her own partner, for the sake of memory</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The text is otherwise unknown, published by Calderone on the basis of autopsy and with a photograph of a what appears to be a squeeze in the publication.</p>
            </div>
